Authors of cpp2html.
See also the files THANKS and ChangeLog.

Lorenzo Bettini <lorenzo.bettini@penteres.it> 
designed and implemented cpp2html; cpp2html is based
on a modification of java2html, also by Lorenzo Bettini..

Jari Korva <jari.korva@iki.fi> added CSS output to java2html,
and this feature is used in cpp2html as well.